{"tid":1299637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「市民谷住道氣」 曾鈺成倡重啟政改","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:27:56.000Z","uid":66811,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c31777768c3d399b7daa04efdcb31bc1d577e944","tid":1299637,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:09:37.000Z","msg":"「市民谷住道氣」 曾鈺成倡重啟政改<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190709/s00001/1562610020907/%E3%80%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%B0%B7%E4%BD%8F%E9%81%93%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E9%88%BA%E6%88%90%E5%80%A1%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E6%94%BF%E6%94%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190709%2Fs00001%2F1562610020907%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2588%25BA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2595%259F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2594%25B9&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1ZWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=afa24509\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190709%2Fs00001%2F1562610020907%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2588%25BA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2595%259F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2594%25B9&h=38a1b32c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190709/s00001/1562610020907/%E3%80%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%B0%B7%E4%BD%8F%E9%81%93%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E9%88%BA%E6%88%90%E5%80%A1%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E6%94%BF%E6%94%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n曾建議修例草案「直上大會」的曾鈺成，昨接受民主黨前主席劉慧卿網台節目訪問時表示，不覺得特首林鄭月娥下台會解決現時問題，又稱「無人可以做得比林鄭更好」，又形容現時政府面對的管治危機是「前所未有」。<br />\n<br />\n「林鄭下台無用 無人可做更好」<br />\n曾鈺成表示，7月1日晚發生衝擊立法會事件後，雖然很多人表明不認同暴力行為，但又表示理解示威者動機，認為與大批市民上街遊行原因一樣，都是「谷住道氣」，一半源自制度不公。<br />\n<br />\n他稱2014至15年政改談判失敗後，政府至今未再推出普選時間表，令市民看不到前景；又說近日有不少聲音認為重啟政改勢惹政治爭拗，包括全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳，但他反問，「是否將問題掃落地氈底就會無了件事」，認為至少應重新與市民建立溝通渠道，但如何做就應交由政府決定。"},{"pid":"59cc49c35a1d78cf7e992be2a16dc25cf839141f","tid":1299637,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:14:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a50184f8a928d6415ef5a2d3eaf6f4a4ab236547","tid":1299637,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfbeb929399f52ab74fcdea05b31e1e796312e3","tid":1299637,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:05:07.000Z","msg":"曾特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾俊華 曾老鼠 全部都係好人"},{"pid":"f489f4833b0be73a6755f3d08ad85721277fcd39","tid":1299637,"uid":148987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"食屎啦死共狗扮好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f8f26f17f3ddc3ba994c0e851b0c4570f7ac07","tid":1299637,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:06:57.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\